    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.07]" style="background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, #8B5CF6 0px, #8B5CF6 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 12px); background-size: 40px 40px;"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-purple-500/5 rounded-tl-[120px]"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 py-16 sm:py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-7xl">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <span class="text-violet-600 font-black text-sm tracking-widest uppercase">E-Commerce Guide</span>
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black leading-[0.85] tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-8">
            <span class="block">E-COMMERCE</span>
            <span class="block text-[#8B5CF6] mt-2">BUILDERS</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-700 font-medium max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
            Sell products online with the right platform. After 142 e-commerce build tests, here's what actually drives sales.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm border-2 border-violet-300 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">
              <span class="text-violet-600 font-black">9.5/10</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-sm">Shopify E-commerce</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm border-2 border-violet-300 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">
              <span class="text-violet-600 font-black">-23%</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-sm">Cart Abandonment</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm border-2 border-violet-300 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">
              <span class="text-violet-600 font-black">2.8x</span>
