            <span class="text-violet-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Shopify cart abandonment is 23% lower than AI builders</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Shopify store: 68% abandonment. Squarespace store: 91% abandonment. Checkout friction kills sales. Trust signals matter.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-violet-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
