              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Product A: photos only. Conversion: 1.9%. Product B: 30-second video. Conversion: 5.3%. Video shows what photos can't.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-violet-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Free shipping threshold increases AOV 47%</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Store A: $5 shipping always. Avg order: $38. Store B: free shipping over $75. Avg order: $56. Customers upgrade to qualify.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-violet-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">3 product photos beats 7 photos</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Product A: 2 photos. Conversion: 2.1%. Product B: 7 photos. Conversion: 2.3%. Product C: 3 strategic angles. Conversion: 4.1%. Quality beats quantity.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-violet-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Mobile checkout friction loses 67% of sales</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Tracked 12,000 mobile sessions. Checkout abandonment: 67%. Desktop abandonment: 41%. Mobile checkout UX = revenue difference.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
