            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-orange-600 mt-1">●</span><span><strong>BigCommerce:</strong> No transaction fees, enterprise features</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-orange-600 mt-1">●</span><span><strong>10Web:</strong> WordPress flexibility with WooCommerce</span></li>
          </ul>
