            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-orange-600 mt-1">●</span><span><strong>Order management:</strong> Order tracking, status updates</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Nice-to-Have Features</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-orange-600 mt-1">●</span><span><strong>Abandoned cart recovery:</strong> Email customers who left items</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-orange-600 mt-1">●</span><span><strong>Product reviews:</strong> Customer testimonials and ratings</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-orange-600 mt-1">●</span><span><strong>Discount codes:</strong> Coupons, promotions, sales</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-orange-600 mt-1">●</span><span><strong>Multi-channel selling:</strong> Social media, marketplace integration</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-orange-600 mt-1">●</span><span><strong>Analytics:</strong> Sales tracking, conversion insights</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-orange-600 mt-1">●</span><span><strong>Live chat:</strong> Customer support during shopping</span></li>
